description:
This is a 360 minute workout called 'Chris Bumstead Bodybuilding 2025 Motivation - Gym & Fitness - Workout' from the channel Steven Goris.
The workout falls under Cardio/Running and Cardio/Treadmill.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You won't need any equipmentThe workout has a The Warrior Workout and The Firestarter vibe.
The The Warrior Workout vibe means Unleash your inner beast. Sweat-dripping, heart-pounding, primal energy. This is especially good for Days when you want to destroy stress and feel invincible. The The Firestarter vibe means Fast, explosive, and electrifying. Short but devastating. This is especially good for When you only have 10-20 minutes but want to give 1000%..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Light and Moderate.
